<template>
	<el-row>
		<el-col :span="24">
			<el-table height="650" :data="notices" border>
				<el-table-column type="index" label="序号" width="80"></el-table-column>
				<el-table-column prop="ReceiverName" label="接收者"></el-table-column>
				<el-table-column prop="MessageDate" label="发送消息时间"></el-table-column>
				<!-- <el-table-column prop="CardID" label="身份证"></el-table-column> -->
				<el-table-column prop="MessageTitle" label="消息类型"></el-table-column>
				<el-table-column prop="MessageContent" label="消息内容"></el-table-column>
			</el-table>
			<el-pagination
				style="margin:10px 0;"
				background
				layout="total, sizes, prev, pager, next, jumper"
				:page-sizes="[20,50,100,200]"
				:page-size="20"
				:total="total"
			></el-pagination>
		</el-col>
	</el-row>
</template>

<script>
	export default{
		data(){
			return {
				notices:[],
				PageSize: 20,
				Page: 1,
				total: 0,
				search:"",
			}
		},
		methods:{
			async getDatas(){
				let params = {
					page: this.Page,
					PageSize: this.PageSize
				}
				let res = await this.$api.get("/Medical/QueryMessages",params)
				this.notices = res.Data.DataList;
				this.total = res.Data.TotalCount;
			}
		},
		mounted() {
			this.getDatas();
		}
	}
</script>

<style>
</style>
